s It Gets》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Mitski-and-Katie-Gavin.-Credit_-Dave-Simpson_WireImage-and-Natasha-Moustache_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="米茨基和凯蒂·加文。图片来源：Dave Simpson/WireImage 和 Natasha Moustache/Getty Images" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Mitski-and-Katie-Gavin.-Credit_-Dave-Simpson_WireImage-and-Natasha-Moustache_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Mitski-and-Katie-Gavin.-Credit_-Dave-Simpson_WireImage-and-Natasha-Moustache_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Mitski-and-Katie-Gavin.-Credit_-Dave-Simpson_WireImage-and-Natasha-Moustache_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Mitski-and-Katie-Gavin.-Credit_-Dave-Simpson_WireImage-and-Natasha-Moustache_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Mitski-and-Katie-Gavin.-Credit_-Dave-Simpson_WireImage-and-Natasha-Moustache_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Mitski-and-Katie-Gavin.-Credit_-Dave-Simpson_WireImage-and-Natasha-Moustache_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/MUNA">MUNA</a>的凯蒂·加文 (Katie Gavin) 向歌迷们展示了她即将推出的首张个人专辑中与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mitski">Mitski</a>合作的《As Good As It Gets》。看看下面。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/muna-cover-interview-2022-self-titled-3354127"><em>NME</em>大读物 – MUNA：“我们相信人们应该在能找到自由和爱的地方度过时光”</a></strong></li></ul><p>在周六（7 月 27 日）纽波特民谣音乐节上的独奏演出中，加文首次表演了《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/munas-katie-gavin-announces-debut-solo-album-what-a-relief-with-tender-single-aftertaste-and-details-of-us-tour-and-london-show-3777220">What A Relief</a> 》中的六首歌曲，这将是她的首张个人唱片。</p><p>在音乐节上首次亮相的歌曲包括她的新单曲《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/munas-katie-gavin-announces-debut-solo-single-aftertaste-3776138">Aftertaste</a> 》和《As Good As It Gets》——加文<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/munas-katie-gavin-announces-debut-solo-album-what-a-relief-with-tender-single-aftertaste-and-details-of-us-tour-and-london-show-3777220">上周在分享专辑曲目列表时透露，这首歌将由米茨基演唱</a>。</p><p>这首歌是对简单爱情的浪漫颂歌，歌词是： <em>“想让你让我失望/断断续续直到我们老/我在里面叠衣服/你在外面修理软管。”</em>由于米茨基没有出席音乐节，加文的 MUNA 乐队成员娜奥米·麦克弗森 (Naomi McPherson) 介入演唱了她的歌曲。</p><p>您可以查看下面的视频。 </p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f6a8.png" alt="🚨" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />有关 Mitski 新功能的信息！</p><p>凯蒂·加文昨晚表演了这首歌，并演唱了米茨基的部分！下面的片段被认为是米茨基的诗句。</p><p> “希望你让我失望/断断续续，直到我们老了/我在里面叠衣服/你在外面修理软管” <a href="https://t.co/0Z68eNpwhh">pic.twitter.com/0Z68eNpwhh</a></p><p> - mitski 数据 (@mitskidata) <a href="https://twitter.com/mitskidata/status/1817224886739165700?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 7 月 27 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="tiktok-embed" cite="https://www.tiktok.com/@flurtyandthriving/video/7396429426671619370" data-video-id="7396429426671619370" data-embed-from="oembed" style="max-width:605px; min-width:325px;"><section> <a target="_blank" title="@flurtyandthriving" href="https://www.tiktok.com/@flurtyandthriving?refer=embed">@flurtyandthriving</a></p><p>回复@edith <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f353.png" alt="🍓" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f490.png" alt="💐" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />所以这件事发生了。什么？？？？？ <a title="穆纳" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/muna?refer=embed">#muna</a> <a title="凡伊斯穆纳" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.co